title: Biden to Undergo Routine Physical Exam Friday
sub_head: Examination will be his first as president
body:
WASHINGTONâ€”President Biden will travel to Walter Reed Medical Center on Friday morning for a routine annual physical examination, according to the White House, his first such exam as president.
Mr. Biden, who turns 79 years old on Saturday, is the oldest serving U.S. president in history.
